{"tid":1831864,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎 、沙士新藥","createTime":"2020-01-20T17:04:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T07:48:35.000Z","uid":299394,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bb81f4896d24b6e7768f1965569e4c8991630467","tid":1831864,"uid":299394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T17:04:09.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎、沙士冠狀病毒暫無藥可醫。<br />\n<br />\n有一種藥，名叫Methisoprinol , 又名 inosine pranobex/ Isoprinosine, 香港註冊藥名為Imin tab 益冒(HK-34682)，由台灣永信藥行出品，為一種免疫促進劑（immunomodulatory), 透過增長自身免疫力，抵抗病毒，在臨床上於 各種病毒感染，如疱疹病毒(herpes virus),水痘病毒（varicella zoster),流感（influenza virus), 生殖器疣病毒（HPV virus) 。<br />\n<br />\n1）<a href=\"https://info.fda.gov.tw/MLMS/ShowFile.aspx?LicId=01031309&amp;Seq=006&amp;Type=9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finfo.fda.gov.tw%2FMLMS%2FShowFile.aspx%3FLicId%3D01031309%26Seq%3D006%26Type%3D9&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=6e1db67f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://info.fda.gov.tw/MLMS/ShowFile.aspx?LicId=01031309&amp;Seq=006&amp;Type=9</a><br />\n2）<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/异丙肌苷\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbaike.baidu.com%2Fitem%2F%E5%BC%82%E4%B8%99%E8%82%8C%E8%8B%B7&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=65772778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://baike.baidu.com/item/异丙肌苷</a><br />\n3）<a href=\"http://www.valentapharm.com/eng/normomed_syrup/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.valentapharm.com%2Feng%2Fnormomed_syrup%2F&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=fbfc079b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.valentapharm.com/eng/normomed_syrup/</a><br />\n4）<a href=\"https://neosine.pl/en/products/neosine-forte/neosine-forte-syrup/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fneosine.pl%2Fen%2Fproducts%2Fneosine-forte%2Fneosine-forte-syrup%2F&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=e1d03f89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://neosine.pl/en/products/neosine-forte/neosine-forte-syrup/</a><br />\n雖然還需進一步研究證明其效果，此藥亦未得到FDA 美國食品藥物管理局認可，在非典型肺炎沒有藥可用的情況下，可考慮施用此 副作用輕微、安全性高的藥物。劑量為50mg/kg per day, 一歲以上小孩可用。<br />\n<br />\n（本人為一家庭醫生，曾用過這種藥很多次於各種年齡（1歲以上）不同病毒感染的人，如手足口病，流感服用特敏福仍高燒不退、生蛇、椰菜花、水痘、呼吸合胞病毒（RSV)等病人，發現功效不錯，希望 各地各位同業、專家 在此疫症 來勢洶洶時可考慮 不妨一試 益冒這種 增強病人免疫力的藥物。"},{"pid":"bfcace982dbd8be3bebf1c32b59a8fa33530812d","tid":1831864,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T17:11:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828784357d77d5b37cacebccf806c7cc48db0b79","tid":1831864,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T17:13:04.000Z","msg":"樓主好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890fffa85c830f2b88143b112e7523d065be90c2","tid":1831864,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T17:16:37.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cd368448c39984590b4f07631302e22a4ffe5ec","tid":1831864,"uid":224632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T17:27:11.000Z","msg":"想知更多<br />\n<br />\n姐係食黎預防，定係感染後食係有用？"},{"pid":"7fc7f71fba90195cfb5285435c2581b9cc430a14","tid":1831864,"uid":299394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cd368448c39984590b4f07631302e22a4ffe5ec","tid":1831864,"uid":224632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T17:27:11.000Z","msg":"想知更多<br />\n<br />\n姐係食黎預防，定係感染後食係有用？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T17:28:20.000Z","msg":"通常感染後先開，增強自身免疫系統，對抗病毒。"},{"pid":"3bceee2c398ecd65d64444a847e3a3115935010e","tid":1831864,"uid":224632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fc7f71fba90195cfb5285435c2581b9cc430a14","tid":1831864,"uid":299394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cd368448c39984590b4f07631302e22a4ffe5ec","tid":1831864,"uid":224632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T17:27:11.000Z","msg":"想知更多<br />\n<br />\n姐係食黎預防，定係感染後食係有用？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T17:28:20.000Z","msg":"通常感染後先開，增強自身免疫系統，對抗病毒。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T17:29:50.000Z","msg":"感謝樓主 記低佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83c3b77defe179d613a5b5d6dcbaa1357b326b5","tid":1831864,"uid":81273,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T17:35:50.000Z","msg":"fda唔批都開到俾病人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b103de5a44c28a7bf0059ead153c2705442d5a","tid":1831864,"uid":299394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b83c3b77defe179d613a5b5d6dcbaa1357b326b5","tid":1831864,"uid":81273,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T17:35:50.000Z","msg":"fda唔批都開到俾病人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T17:38:22.000Z","msg":"因為香港有註冊，歐州、台灣、俄羅斯都有藥廠出同有indication, 當然唔係first line"},{"pid":"88bfa4742596f8f190aff45e5ca3820e71bb4933","tid":1831864,"uid":194326,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T21:54:03.000Z","msg":"當年爆沙士都大把tamiflu script 添<br />\n但問題係隻野冇neuraminidase 丫嘛<br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔信你，SARS / MERS 用過嘅藥我都睇過<br />\n就係冇見過你呢隻<br />\n整份literature 睇睇啦<br />\n<br />\n香港醫生用百度reference ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fb2d94bcd51b56866663a9a7e0d767b6d0ac19","tid":1831864,"uid":194326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T21:56:34.000Z","msg":"禁曬啲links 睇過，呢個post有古怪下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af02ae1b54969bc9b79d9f997be0f998d4ec0df","tid":1831864,"uid":55851,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T22:20:31.000Z","msg":"又係啲藥廠sales扮醫生開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從未見過醫生會叫人自己買藥食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad2279f84a775cfcbd5ebc64b143a2b76313eb5","tid":1831864,"uid":106215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T22:37:26.000Z","msg":"Off-label indication 都要有trial support 呱？如果冇trial，唔通連Case study 都冇？"},{"pid":"042ef997b1e64cf52824942c07a8772e6e710e9f","tid":1831864,"uid":299394,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bb81f4896d24b6e7768f1965569e4c8991630467","tid":1831864,"uid":299394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T17:04:09.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎、沙士冠狀病毒暫無藥可醫。<br />\n<br />\n有一種藥，名叫Methisoprinol , 又名 inosine pranobex/ Isoprinosine, 香港註冊藥名為Imin tab 益冒(HK-34682)，由台灣永信藥行出品，為一種免疫促進劑（immunomodulatory), 透過增長自身免疫力，抵抗病毒，在臨床上於 各種病毒感染，如疱疹病毒(herpes virus),水痘病毒（varicella zoster),流感（influenza virus), 生殖器疣病毒（HPV virus) 。<br />\n<br />\n1）<a href=\"https://info.fda.gov.tw/MLMS/ShowFile.aspx?LicId=01031309&amp;Seq=006&amp;Type=9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finfo.fda.gov.tw%2FMLMS%2FShowFile.aspx%3FLicId%3D01031309%26Seq%3D006%26Type%3D9&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=6e1db67f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://info.fda.gov.tw/MLMS/ShowFile.aspx?LicId=01031309&amp;Seq=006&amp;Type=9</a><br />\n2）<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/异丙肌苷\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbaike.baidu.com%2Fitem%2F%E5%BC%82%E4%B8%99%E8%82%8C%E8%8B%B7&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=65772778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://baike.baidu.com/item/异丙肌苷</a><br />\n3）<a href=\"http://www.valentapharm.com/eng/normomed_syrup/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.valentapharm.com%2Feng%2Fnormomed_syrup%2F&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=fbfc079b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.valentapharm.com/eng/normomed_syrup/</a><br />\n4）<a href=\"https://neosine.pl/en/products/neosine-forte/neosine-forte-syrup/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fneosine.pl%2Fen%2Fproducts%2Fneosine-forte%2Fneosine-forte-syrup%2F&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=e1d03f89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://neosine.pl/en/products/neosine-forte/neosine-forte-syrup/</a><br />\n雖然還需進一步研究證明其效果，此藥亦未得到FDA 美國食品藥物管理局認可，在非典型肺炎沒有藥可用的情況下，可考慮施用此 副作用輕微、安全性高的藥物。劑量為50mg/kg per day, 一歲以上小孩可用。<br />\n<br />\n（本人為一家庭醫生，曾用過這種藥很多次於各種年齡（1歲以上）不同病毒感染的人，如手足口病，流感服用特敏福仍高燒不退、生蛇、椰菜花、水痘、呼吸合胞病毒（RSV)等病人，發現功效不錯，希望 各地各位同業、專家 在此疫症 來勢洶洶時可考慮 不妨一試 益冒這種 增強病人免疫力的藥物。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T01:02:17.000Z","msg":"其實呢隻藥最indicated 係subacute sclerosing panencephalitis (SSPE)<br />\n<br />\n都有些paper for respiratory infection, for health care professions only ,真係好少<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5100179/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5100179%2F&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=0e9f78a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5100179/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s12325-019-00995-6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Farticle%2F10.1007%2Fs12325-019-00995-6&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=e58672e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s12325-019-00995-6</a><br />\n<br />\nBy the way, 出面應該買唔到，HA 應該都冇，有錢都要有牌照先買到<br />\n<br />\n真係first line 唔得先試，想拋磚引玉大家討論下"},{"pid":"c61732f8b73cd6941bed1cc0b129a844eebb210b","tid":1831864,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6af02ae1b54969bc9b79d9f997be0f998d4ec0df","tid":1831864,"uid":55851,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T22:20:31.000Z","msg":"又係啲藥廠sales扮醫生開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從未見過醫生會叫人自己買藥食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T01:12:15.000Z","msg":"扮醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n28(2)<br />\n除第(3)款另有規定外，任何人並非已註冊、臨時註冊或獲豁免註冊而 (b)對某人進行任何醫學診斷、訂明任何醫藥治療或施行任何醫藥治療(包括外科手術)而導致該人受人身傷害，即屬犯罪 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n(i)一經循簡易程序定罪，可處罰款$200,000及監禁3年；或  (由1996年第7號第34條修訂)<br />\n(ii)一經循公訴程序定罪，可處監禁7年。  (由1986年第68號第5條增補)<br />\n<br />\n第161章 《醫生註冊條例》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap161!zh-Hant-HK?xpid=ID_1438402759418_001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap161%21zh-Hant-HK%3Fxpid%3DID_1438402759418_001&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=d40ae482\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap161!zh-Hant-HK?xpid=ID_1438402759418_001</a>"},{"pid":"1face18866bb0c03dadb2565947fa4fcf0c74023","tid":1831864,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"042ef997b1e64cf52824942c07a8772e6e710e9f","tid":1831864,"uid":299394,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bb81f4896d24b6e7768f1965569e4c8991630467","tid":1831864,"uid":299394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T17:04:09.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎、沙士冠狀病毒暫無藥可醫。<br />\n<br />\n有一種藥，名叫Methisoprinol , 又名 inosine pranobex/ Isoprinosine, 香港註冊藥名為Imin tab 益冒(HK-34682)，由台灣永信藥行出品，為一種免疫促進劑（immunomodulatory), 透過增長自身免疫力，抵抗病毒，在臨床上於 各種病毒感染，如疱疹病毒(herpes virus),水痘病毒（varicella zoster),流感（influenza virus), 生殖器疣病毒（HPV virus) 。<br />\n<br />\n1）<a href=\"https://info.fda.gov.tw/MLMS/ShowFile.aspx?LicId=01031309&amp;Seq=006&amp;Type=9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finfo.fda.gov.tw%2FMLMS%2FShowFile.aspx%3FLicId%3D01031309%26Seq%3D006%26Type%3D9&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%